name: magical grid
description:
In celebration of the 20th anniversary of Processing.

Discs are pulsating at constant (but slightly different) speed, creating innumerable continuous patterns.

0 to start over
+ to speed up
- to slow down
6 to enlarge the dots
4 to shrink the dots
1 to invert b&w
2 to stop
3 to start again

interactive sketch | p5js | @wavegrower
